io, giving Mario the ability to fly and access hidden areas. Created specifically as a pick-up-and-play experience that can be instantly enjoyed by players of all skill levels on the Nintendo 3DS system. For the first time, players will also be able to purchase and download the entire game digitally through the Nintendo eShop. A packaged version will also be available.', '106' , '34.99', '2',  '3DS');
