INSERT INTO Items(itemID, itemName, releaseDate, description, gameImageID, price, conditionId, console)         
                                VALUES('1623', 'Super Mario 3D World', '2016-03-14', 'Journey with Mario, Luigi and more to the Sprixie Kingdom in SUPER MARIO 3D WORLD! Bowser has kidnapped the Sprixie Princess, and its up to Mario and his friends to rescue her, racing to the Goal Pole at the end of various stages along the way! The Sprixie Kingdom contains all sorts of troublesome tricks and traps for our heroes to negotiate: transparent pipes to squeeze through, balls to aim and throw at enemies, and moving trains with roofs to ride! There may even be times when they need to clamber over a wall, just like a cat! With four-player local multiplayer and special Wii U GamePad controls, SUPER MARIO 3D WORLD is an all-new adventure thats only available on Wii U!Marios range of headwear  and special abilities  continues to expand! Along with classics such as Tanooki Mario and Boomerang Mario, there are several new power-ups to discover. Pick up a Super Bell to turn Mario into a wall-climbing, claw-scratching cat, wear a Cannon Box on your head to launch projectiles, or collect a Double Cherry to generate a helpful clone so you can attack on the double!This adventure isnt all about Mario, though! Luigi, Princess Peach and Toad are along for the ride too, and they each have different skills and abilities to offer. Mario offers the most balanced set of skills, while Luigi can leap the highest, Princess Peach can hover in mid-air and Toad is the fastest on the ground. Choose whichever character you like and use their unique skills to fully explore every corner of the courses!Up to four people can play together in SUPER MARIO 3D WORLDs local multiplayer mode  work together to clear a stage or compete to see who can get the highest score at the end of each level! A variety of different controllers* can be used, so select the one which best suits your style of play.* Additional accessories required for multiplayer mode, sold separately.Uncover one of the many Stamps hidden throughout the Sprixie Kingdom and you can use it to customise the messages you post to Miiverse from within the game. Have fun collecting them all!Discover a new world rendered in HD in the first ever multiplayer 3D Mario adventurePlay as Mario or a number of other characters, each with their own unique personalitiesRevisit classic power-ups and discover plenty of exciting new abilitiesCollect special Stamps to customise in-game Miiverse posts', '623' , '29.99', '3',  'Wii_U');
INSERT INTO Items(itemID, itemName, releaseDate, description, gameImageID, price, conditionId, console)         
                                VALUES('1624', 'Donkey Kong Country Tropical Freeze', '2016-03-14', 'Donkey Kong Country: Tropical Freeze is the first completely new Donkey Kong side-scrolling action game in three years, exclusively for Wii U!In this adventure, the Kongs must reclaim their island from the dastardly Snowmads of the northern seas. To do this, they need to set off on a journey around five different islands, plus the frozen Donkey Kong Island.This will be the first game in the series to be in HD, bringing glorious detail and expression to the world. Depending on the stage, the camera will move to show the action from dynamic viewpoints, bringing you closer to DK''s world than ever!Along with Diddy Kong, Dixie Kong returns as a main character, while Cranky Kong is playable for the first time! Your abilities change depending on which partner you bring along, opening up new choices and possibilities. Theres even a cooperative two-player mode, with each player controlling one of the characters and working together to progress through the game!A brand new Donkey Kong Country adventure in high-definition!Run, leap, and roll across six different islands on your own or with a partnerUse each character''s unique skills to grab a whole host of collectables', '624' , '29.99', '3',  'Wii_U');
