                                VALUES('1767', 'The Smurfs 2', 'TBD', 'Four-Player Co-op: Play with four players on the screen simultaneously. Jump in and jump out seamlessly. Play as Your Favorite Smurf: Become your favorite Smurf to help bring Smurfette home! The Right Smurf for the Right Job: Mix and match the Smurfs you play as ? Papa can freeze enemies with his magical potions and Vanity can strike a pose to become a temporary platform to reach new heights! Six Worlds to Explore: From the Enchanted Forest to the Spooky Woods, through the streets of New York, to the majestic city of Paris, and everywhere in between.', '767' , '39.99', '2',  'Xbox_360');
