let of Fall''s End, freely explore Montana''s rivers, lands, and skies in true Far Cry style, with more customizable weapons and vehicles than ever before. Carve your own path through a world that reacts to your decisions. Find your own way to survive, thrive, and beat back the forces of oppression. The stakes have never been higher.FEATURES: Fan the flames of resistance and fight to free Hope County from the grip of a deadly cult in the newest installment of the Far Cry series. Beware of the wrath of Joseph Seed and his cult followers as you support the resistance in small-town America. Explore Hope County and discover the Montana countryside, wildlife, and its inhabitants in an exciting open world. Play your way. Build your character, make your own allies, and watch the world change as you progress. Upgrade to the Gold Edition and get immediate access to all Deluxe add-on content, plus the season pass.', '906' , 'N/A', '5',  'Xbox_One');
