INSERT INTO Items(itemID, itemName, releaseDate, description, gameImageID, price, conditionId, console)         
                                VALUES('1934', 'Road Rage', '2017-11-14', 'WHENTHERES NOLAW TO OBEY,THERES NO LAW TO BREAK...In the broken city of Ashen, lines are heavily drawn and being in with the right people could mean the difference between life and death. You are Ace, the newest member of the outlaw motorcycle club controlling Ashen with its underground crime. You have two goals in life: earn lots of money and ride fast.With big dreams to become club president, you set in motion a new strategy to fulfill the goals of the motorcycle gang, using your skill on a bike to propel you into a position of ultimate control. Once president, you can use your crew to chase your own goals.However, challenging authority in Ashen simply isnt done and being reckless could lead you to learn about the real art of war!KEY FEATURES 42 story-based missions 98 total missions 11 unique and upgradable bike models Customizable skins, wheels, weapons, and more 12 unique melee weapons 40 battle moves, ranging from light and fast to slow and powerful Cinematic, slow-mo effects during intense warfare Online leaderboards 4-player online multiplayerUNIQUE POINTS: True open-world gameplay - no limits on where you can go within a race, as long as your bike can handle it Heavy melee-based combat racing, but with a deep story that contains multiple characters Pure motorcycle action - no walking from point to point Varied game modes, some with objectives beyond racing 11 distinct characters', '934' , '39.99', '5',  'Xbox_One');
